PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 1998-05111998-03-260,  HERITAGE,  ,  , 
PrecisOrder authorizing the CANADIAN NATIONAL RAILWAY COMPANY to sell its railway station located in Hamilton, Ontario, on the condition that the purchaser agree to grant a heritage conservation easement to the Ontario Heritage Foundation and that the Canadian flag be flown in perpetuity.
Attachments
precis:
Order authorizing the CANADIAN NATIONAL RAILWAY COMPANY to sell its railway
station located in Hamilton, Ontario, on the condition that the purchaser
agree to grant a heritage conservation easement to the Ontario Heritage
Foundation and that the Canadian flag be flown in perpetuity.
